Product description

For a quick, clean cuppa! Our teabag tongs are shaped like two spoons with the word TEA cut out. Now you can efficiently remove teabags from cups or teapots, easily squeeze excess liquid from teabags and help to avoid scalding tea splashing onto your hand. Simply squeeze the tongs gently together to pick up and remove teabags. Simple yet highly effective!
